                    ],
                    Texts: [
                        {
                            Text: "You are the one who cracked the granary open. Word runs this road faster than any wagon."
                        },
                        {
                            Text: "The Crossroads silo answers to no memo now and the whole caravan breathes easier. Roll on through."
                        },
                        {
                            Text: "The artery is quieter since Crossroads came back. You freed the granary and every teamster on this dust knows it - safe passage, founder or not."
                        }
                    ],
                    Name: "Boro - the caravan breathes",
                    Label: "field_echo"
                },
