                    Texts: [
                        {
                            Text: "Old Caravan road. Sango to Kalahar, the whole map hangs off this dust. I guard the caravans, which means I see every soul on the straight - including you, a bend back."
                        },
                        {
                            Text: "A guard who blinks is a guard who buries a wagon. Stand and settle it - road rules are road rules."
                        },
                        {
                            Text: "This artery runs the length of the region and I watch all of it. You have been in my eyes since the last bend. We battle."
                        }
                    ],
                    Name: "Caravan Guard Boro",
                    Label: "default"
                }
